'''劳氏猪笼草'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Nepenthes lowii}}''）是[[婆罗洲|婆罗洲]][[特有种|特有的]]热带[[食虫植物|食虫植物]]。<ref name="夏洛特2007">{{cite book | title=[[食蟲植物觀賞&栽培圖鑑|食蟲植物觀賞&栽培圖鑑]] | publisher=商周出版 | author=夏洛特 | year=2007 | location=台北 | pages=58-59 | isbn=978-986-124-850-9}}</ref>其得名于在[[基纳巴卢山|基纳巴卢山]]发现劳氏猪笼草的[[休·洛|休·洛]]。劳氏猪笼草是[[猪笼草属|猪笼草属]]较为特殊的物种，其上位笼强烈收缩，唇大大缩窄，笼盖的下表面具有许多毛鬚。<ref name="夏洛特2007" /><ref name=Clarke>Clarke, C.M. 1997. ''[[婆罗洲的猪笼草属植物|Nepenthes of Borneo]]''. [[自然历史出版社_(婆罗洲)|Natural History Publications (Borneo)]], Kota Kinabalu.</ref>

== 植物学史 ==
=== 命名与发现 ===
1851年3月，身为[[英国|英国]]殖民行政官员和博物学家的[[休·洛|休·洛]]在[[基纳巴卢山|基纳巴卢山]]的山坡上发现劳氏猪笼草。休·洛在他的记录中这样写道：{{refn|[[休·洛|休·洛]]对基纳巴卢山的山坡上发现的劳氏猪笼草的描述原文：<ref name=P&L />{{Cquote|A little way further we came upon a most extraordinary ''Nepenthes'', of, I believe, a hitherto unknown form, the mouth being oval and large, the neck exceedingly contracted so as to appear funnel-shaped, and at right angles to the body of the pitcher, which was large, swollen out laterally, flattened above and sustained in an horizontal position by the strong prolongation of the midrib of the plant as in other species. It is a very strong growing kind and absolutely covered with its interesting pitchers, each of which contains little less than a pint of water and all of them were full to the brim, so admirably were they sustained by the supporting petiole. The plants were generally upwards of 40 ft long, but I could find no young ones nor any flowers, not even traces of either.}}|name=P&L|group="注"}}<ref name=P&L>Phillipps, A. & A. Lamb 1996. ''[[婆罗洲的猪笼草|Pitcher-Plants of Borneo]]''. [[自然历史出版社_(婆罗洲)|Natural History Publications (Borneo)]], Kota Kinabalu.</ref>

{{Cquote|我们一点点来认识这个不同寻常的猪笼草吧，我相信这是迄今为止未曾见过的猪笼草形态。其笼口为椭圆形，非常巨大。笼身中部剧烈的收缩成漏斗状，笼身下部膨大，扁平，与笼口成直角，与地面水平。与其他猪笼草一样，其捕虫笼由中脉强烈的延伸而来。其是一种长势强健的种类，也觉得包含了其有趣的捕虫笼。其每个捕虫笼内都装有不超过1品脱的液体，神奇的是，这些叶柄竟能经得住这些满当当的笼子。其植株通常可长达40厘米，但我没有找到幼苗及带有花序或有迹象要开花的植株。
}}

劳氏猪笼草的[[模式标本|模式标本]]由休·洛采集于[[基纳巴卢山|基纳巴卢山]]，其编号为“''Low s.n.''”，存放于[[邱园|英国皇家植物园]]中。<ref name=Schlauer>Schlauer, J. N.d. ''[http://www.omnisterra.com/bot/cp_home.cgi?name=Nepenthes+lowii&submit=Submit+Query&search=all Nepenthes lowii]''. Carnivorous Plant Database.</ref>

1859年，[[约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克|约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克]]正式描述{{refn|1859年，[[约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克|约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克]]对于劳氏猪笼草的原始描述：<ref name=Hooker1859 />{{Cquote|{{nbsp|6}}''Ascidia magna, curva, basi inflata, medio constricta, dein ampliata, infundibuliformia; ore maximo, latissimo, annulo O.''<br>
{{nbsp|6}}Nepenthes Lowii, H. f.—Caule robusto tereti, foliis crasse coriaceis, longe crasse petiolatis lineari-oblongis, ascidiis magnis curvis basi ventricosis medio valde constrictis, ore maximo ampliato, annulo O, operculo oblongo intus dense longe setoso. (''Tab.'' LXXI.)<br>
{{nbsp|6}}''Hab.''—Kina Balu; alt. 6,000–8,000 feet (''Low'').<br>
{{nbsp|6}}A noble species, with very remarkable pitchers, quite unlike those of any other species. They are curved, 4–10 inches long, swollen at the base, then much constricted, and suddenly dilating to a broad, wide, open mouth, with glossy shelving inner walls, and a minute row of low tubercles round the circumference; they are of a bright pea green, mottled inside with purple. The leaves closely resemble those of ''Edwardsiana'' and ''Boschiana'' in size, form, and texture, but are more linear-oblong.<br>
{{nbsp|6}}I have specimens of what are sent as the male flower and fruit, but not being attached, I have not ventured to describe them as such. The male raceme is eight inches long, dense flowered. Peduncles simple. Perianth with depressed glands on the inner surface, externally rufous and pubescent. Column long and slender. ''Female'' inflorescence: a very dense oblong panicle; rachis, peduncles, perianth, and fruit-covered with rusty tomentum. Capsules, two-thirds of an inch long, one-sixth of an inch broad.}}|name=Hooker|group="注"}}了劳氏猪笼草。<ref name=Hooker1859 />约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克的原始描述和插图刊登于[[斯宾塞·圣约翰|斯宾塞·圣约翰]]于1862年出版的《远东森林生活》{{small|（''Life in the Forests of the Far East''）}}中。<ref name=John>St. John, S. 1862. ''Life in the Forests of the Far East; or, Travels in northern Borneo''. 2 volumes. Smith, Elder & Co., London.</ref>关于基纳巴卢山的劳氏猪笼草斯宾塞·圣约翰这样写道：{{refn|斯宾塞·圣约翰对基纳巴卢山的劳氏猪笼草的描述原文：<ref name=John />{{Cquote|We soon came upon the magnificent pitcher-plant, the ''Nepenthes Lowii'', which Mr. Low was anxious to obtain. We could find no young plants, but took cuttings, which the natives said would grow. [...] We at last reached a narrow, rocky ridge, covered with brushwood, but with thousands of plants of the beautiful ''Nepenthes Lowii'' growing among them. [...] We sent our men on next morning to wait for us at the cave, while we stayed behind to collect specimens of the ''Nepenthes Lowii'' and the ''Nepenthes Villosa''. The former is, in my opinion, the loveliest of them all, and its shape is most elegant. [...] The outside colour of the pitchers is a bright pea-green, the inside dark mahogany; the lid is green, while the glandular are mahogany-coloured. A very elegant claret jug might be made of this shape.}}|name=John|group="注"}}<ref name=John />

{{Cquote|我们很快就来到休·洛先生急于得到的劳氏猪笼草面前。我们找不到幼苗，只能剪取一些枝条，当地人这些枝条也可以存活。……最后我们来到一个长满灌木的狭窄山脊上，这里差不多生长着上千棵劳氏猪笼草。……我们让其他人第二天早上在山洞那碰头，而我们留下来采集劳氏猪笼草和长毛猪笼草的标本。在我看来，劳氏猪笼草是所有猪笼草中最讨人喜欢的，其捕虫笼的外形特别典雅。……劳氏猪笼草捕虫笼的外表面为浅豆绿色，内表面为暗红褐色，笼盖为绿色并覆有红褐色的蜜腺。其形状就像一个典雅的葡萄酒壶。
}}

{{double image|right|Nepenthes lowii Life in the forests of the Far East.png|200|Nepenthes lowii Macfarlane illustration.jpg|180|《远东森林的生活》中劳氏猪笼草上位笼的插图（左），麦克法兰专著中劳氏猪笼草的线条画（右）}}

随后的几年间，许多著名的植物学家都在各大出版物上介绍了劳氏猪笼草，如[[弗里德里希·安东·威廉·米克尔|弗里德里希·安东·威廉·米克尔]]{{small|（1870）}}<ref>Miquel, F.A.G. 1870. ''Nepenthes''. ''Illustrations de la flore l'Archipel Indien'' '''1''': 1–48.</ref>、[[约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克|约瑟夫·道尔顿·胡克]]{{small|（1873）}}<ref>{{la icon}} Hooker, J.D. 1873. [[猪笼草科_(1873年专著)|Ordo CLXXV bis. Nepenthaceæ]]. In: A. de Candolle ''[[Prodromus_Systematis_Naturalis_Regni_Vegetabilis|Prodromus Systematis Naturalis Regni Vegetabilis]]'' '''17''': 90–105.</ref>、[[弗雷德里克·威廉·伯比奇|弗雷德里克·威廉·伯比奇]]{{small|（1882）}}<ref name=Burbidge>Burbidge, F.W. 1882. [http://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/25598125 Notes on the new ''Nepenthes''] {{Wayback|url=http://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/25598125 |date=20120515231903 }}. ''[[园丁纪事|The Gardeners' Chronicle]]'', new series, '''17'''(420): 56.</ref>、[[奥多阿多·贝卡利|奥多阿多·贝卡利]]{{small|（1886）}}<ref>Beccari, O. 1886. Rivista delle specie del genere ''Nepenthes''. ''Malesia'' '''3''': 1–15.</ref>、[[恩斯特·温施曼|恩斯特·温施曼]]{{small|（Ernst Wunschmann，1891）}}<ref>Wunschmann, E. 1891. Nepenthaceae. In: A. Engler & K. Prantl. ''Die natürlichen Pflanzenfamilien'' '''3'''(2): 253–260.</ref>、[[奥托·施塔普夫|奥托·施塔普夫]]{{small|（1894）}}<ref>Stapf, O. 1894. On the flora of Mount Kinabalu, in North Borneo. ''The Transactions of the Linnean Society of London'' '''4''': 96–263.</ref>、[[哈里·维奇|哈里·维奇]]{{small|（1897）}}<ref>Veitch, H.J. 1897. ''Nepenthes''. ''Journal of the Royal Horticultural Society'' '''21'''(2): 226–255.</ref>、[[雅各布·海斯伯特·博尔拉吉|雅各布·海斯伯特·博尔拉吉]]{{small|（Jacob Gijsbert Boerlage，1900）}}<ref>Boerlage, J.G. 1900. ''Nepenthes''. In: ''Handleiding tot de kennis der flora van Nederlandsch Indië'', Volume 3, Part 1. pp. 53–54.</ref>和[[埃尔默·德鲁·美林|埃尔默·德鲁·美林]]{{small|（1921）}}<ref>Merrill, E.D. 1921. A bibliographic enumeration of Bornean plants. ''Journal of the Straits branch of the Royal Asiatic Society'', special number. pp. 281–295.</ref>。但是，大部分出版物只是简单的提到了劳氏猪笼草。1895年，分类学家[[君特·贝克·冯·曼那哥塔-勒驰奈|君特·贝克·冯·曼那哥塔-勒驰奈]]首先对劳氏猪笼草进行了分类。因其不同寻常的捕虫笼形态特征，他将劳氏猪笼草独立为一组——[[猪笼草属分类学|网纹猪笼草组]]{{small|（''Retiferae''）}}。<ref name=Beck>{{de icon}} Beck, G. 1895. [[猪笼草属_(专著)|Die Gattung ''Nepenthes'']]. ''Wiener Illustrirte Garten-Zeitung'' '''20'''(3–6): 96–107, 141–150, 182–192, 217–229.</ref>

[[约翰·缪尔黑德·麦克法兰|约翰·缪尔黑德·麦克法兰]]在其1908年的专著《[[猪笼草科_(1908年专著)|猪笼草科]]》中发表了修改后的描述和插图。<ref name=Macfarlane>Macfarlane, J.M. 1908. [[猪笼草科_(1908年专著)|Nepenthaceae]]. In: A. Engler. ''Das Pflanzenreich IV'', III, Heft 36: 1–91.</ref>此外，约翰·缪尔黑德·麦克法兰还在1914年的《林奈学会杂志》{{small|（''Journal of the Linnean Society''）}}<ref>Macfarlane, J.M. 1914. Nepenthaceae. In: L.S. Gibbs. A contribution to the flora and the plant formations of Mount Kinabalu and the Highlands of British North Borneo. ''Journal of the Linnean Society'' '''42''': 125–127.</ref>和1919年的《园艺标准百科全书》{{small|（''The Standard Cyclopedia of Horticulture''）}}<ref>Macfarlane, J.M. 1919. ''Nepenthes''. In: L.H. Bailey. ''The Standard Cyclopedia of Horticulture'', Volume 4. pp. 2122–2130.</ref>上发表了关于劳氏猪笼草的文章。

1927年，荷兰植物学家[[B·H·丹瑟|B·H·丹瑟]]在《热带大自然》{{small|（''De Tropische Natuur''）}}中发表了一份新的劳氏猪笼草图解。<ref>Danser, B.H. 1927. Indische bekerplanten. ''De Tropische Natuur'' '''16''': 197–205.</ref>次年，B·H·丹瑟在他的开拓性专著《[[荷属东印度群岛的猪笼草科植物|荷属东印度群岛的猪笼草科植物]]》中提供了劳氏猪笼草的拉丁判别法{{refn|[[B·H·丹瑟|B·H·丹瑟]]的专著中对劳氏猪笼草的[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]判别法：<ref name=Danser />{{Cquote|''Folia mediocria'' petiolata, lamina lanceolata v. oblonga, nervis longitudinalibus utrinque c. 3, vagina caulis c. 2/3 amplectente ; ''ascidia rosularum'' et ''inferiora'' ignota ; ''ascidia superiora'' magna, parte inferiore globosa, medio valde constricta, os versus infundibuliformia, costis 2 elevatis, ore expanso operculum versus acuto, peristomio 0, operculo oblongo facie inferiore setis crassis longis, prope basin carina crassa obtusa ; ''inflorescentia'' racemus longus pedicellis c. 25 mm longis omnibus 2-floris ; ''indumentum'' in partibus iuvenilibus parcum tomentosum v. hirsutum, denique subnullum.}}|name=Danser1|group="注"}}及植物学描述。<ref name=Danser>Danser, B.H. 1928. [[荷属东印度群岛的猪笼草科植物|The Nepenthaceae of the Netherlands Indies]]. ''Bulletin du Jardin Botanique de Buitenzorg'', Série III, '''9'''(3–4): 249–438.</ref>

=== 新的原生地 ===
在基纳巴卢山发现劳氏猪笼草后不久，1922年，[[埃里克·米约贝里|埃里克·米约贝里]]又在[[巴杜拉威山|巴杜拉威山]]和[[毛律山|毛律山]]发现了劳氏猪笼草。<ref name=Mjoberg>Mjöberg, E. 1925. An Expedition to the Kalabit Country and Mt. Murud, Sarawak. ''Geographical Review'' '''15'''(3): 411–427. {{DOI|10.2307/208563}}</ref>埃里克·米约贝里在他对毛律山的记录中这样写道：{{refn|埃里克·米约贝里对毛律山的记录原文：<ref name=Mjoberg /><ref name=Beaman />{{Cquote|We found ourselves in a strange landscape where low bushes with thick leathery leaves constituted the predominating vegetation. Here and there smaller trees were seen, among them a conifer with trunk and larger branches practically covered with the yellow blossoms of a small, richly flowering, epiphytic orchid. Bright scarlet or snow-white flowers of rhododendron and similar plants were met with everywhere; and most noticeable were the enormous and characteristically shaped pitchers of ''Nepenthes lowii'', hitherto recorded only from Kinabalu and Batu Lawi.}}|name=Mjoberg|group="注"}}<ref name=Mjoberg /><ref name=Beaman>Beaman, J.H. 1999. {{PDFlink|[http://www.arbec.com.my/pdf/art3mayjun99.pdf Preliminary enumeration of the summit flora, Mount Murud, Kelabit Highlands, Sarawak.]|99.4 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 101826 bytes -->}} ''ASEAN Review of Biodiversity and Environmental Conservation'': 1–23.</ref>

{{Cquote|我们发现我们现在身处于一个奇怪的环境中，其中具革质厚叶的灌木为优势植被。随处可见小型的树木，针叶树的树干和树枝上了附生着大量开着黄色小花的附生兰。开着鲜红或雪白花朵的杜鹃及开着类似花朵的植物到处都是；但最令人瞩目的还是只有在基纳巴卢山和巴杜拉威山才能看到的劳氏猪笼草的巨大笼子。
}}

在考察期间，埃里克·米约贝里在毛律山采集到了劳氏猪笼草的标本，其编号为“''Mjöberg 115''”。<ref name=Beaman />1926年，埃里克·米约贝里又在[[太本山|太本山]]{{small|（Bukit Batu Tiban）}}的东北坡上发现了劳氏猪笼草，但没有在这里采集标本。<ref name=Danser />

1995年4月10日至17日，[[约翰·H·比曼|约翰·H·比曼]]在毛律山顶峰山脊海拔2300米至2400米处采集到了另一份标本，其编号为“''Beaman 11476''”。<ref name=Beaman />这份标本采集自1922年埃里克·米约贝里对毛律山的首次考察后的第八次植物学考察中。<ref name=Beaman />

=== 错误的鉴定 ===
尽管劳氏猪笼草的捕虫笼具有独特的外形，但[[伯特伦·伊夫林·斯迈西斯|伯特伦·伊夫林·斯迈西斯]]曾将其暂时归为[[西马来西亚|西马来西亚]]特有的[[麦克法兰猪笼草|麦克法兰猪笼草]]{{small|（''N. macfarlanei''）}}<ref name=Schlauer />，但他也表示其可能是一个新的物种<ref name=Kurata />。这个错误的鉴定发表在1965年于[[古晋|古晋]]举行的联合国教科文组织热带湿地研讨会{{small|（UNESCO Humid Tropics Symposium）}}上<ref name=Smythies1965 />，而该报告是基于1963年7月，[[爱丽丝·希拉·达顿·科莱尼特|爱丽丝·希拉·达顿·科莱尼特]]{{small|（Iris Sheila Darnton Collenette）}}在[[马西劳|东马西劳河]]<ref name=Kurata />采集的标本作出的。<ref>van Steenis-Kruseman, M.J., ''et al.'' 2006. [http://www.nationaalherbarium.nl/FMCollectors/D/DarntonIS.htm Cyclopaedia of Malesian Collectors: Iris Sheila Darnton Collenette]. Nationaal Herbarium Nederland.</ref>之所以会将它们混淆，是因为劳氏猪笼草下位笼的笼盖下表面具长须且其唇较发达，上位笼的唇极窄；而麦克法兰猪笼草笼盖的下表面也具毛须，但实际上比劳氏猪笼草短得多。<ref name=Kurata />

== 形态特征 ==
[[Image:Murud_N._lowii_5.jpg|thumb]]
=== 茎与叶 ===
劳氏猪笼草为[[藤本植物|藤本植物]]。茎呈圆柱形，可长达10米<ref name=P&L />，直径可达20毫米。[[节间距|节间距]]可达8厘米。<ref name=Clarke />

劳氏猪笼草的叶片为[[wikt:革质|革质]]，[[wikt:具柄|具柄]]，呈[[wikt:长圆形|长圆形]]－[[wikt:披针形|披针形]]，可长达30厘米，宽至9厘米。<ref name=Kurata>Kurata, S. 1976. ''[[基纳巴卢山的猪笼草|Nepenthes of Mount Kinabalu]]''. Sabah National Parks Publications No. 2, Sabah National Parks Trustees, Kota Kinabalu.</ref>[[叶尖|叶尖]]圆，[[叶基|叶基]]骤缩。叶柄呈槽状，可长达14厘米。<ref name=Kurata />其包住茎周长的三分之二到五分之四。<ref name=Kurata />[[中脉|中脉]]两侧各有3至4条[[纵脉|纵脉]]。[[羽状脉|羽状脉]]直向延伸或倾斜延伸。[[笼蔓|笼蔓]]可长达20厘米，通常不形成[[笼蔓圈|笼蔓圈]]。<ref name=Clarke />

[[Image:Murud_N._lowii_55.jpg|thumb]]

=== 捕虫笼 ===
劳氏猪笼草[[下位捕虫笼|下位笼]]的下部为球形，中部收缩成葫芦形，上部再扩大。下位笼比上位笼小，高仅可达10厘米，宽尽可达4厘米。因劳氏猪笼草会迅速的进入攀援阶段，所以它的下位笼很少见。腹面的[[笼翼|笼翼]]常仅出现于捕虫笼的上半部。[[猪笼草#唇|唇]]为圆柱形，基部宽大。其可宽达12毫米，具突出的[[唇齿|唇齿]]与[[唇肋|唇肋]]。<ref name=Clarke />内缘部分约占截面表面总长度的62%。<ref name=Baueretal2012>Bauer, U., C.J. Clemente, T. Renner & W. Federle 2012. Form follows function: morphological diversification and alternative trapping strategies in carnivorous ''Nepenthes'' pitcher plants. ''Journal of Evolutionary Biology'' '''25'''(1): 90–102. {{DOI|10.1111/j.1420-9101.2011.02406.x}}</ref>下位笼内表面的下半部覆盖着腺体。<ref name=Clarke />蜡质区稀少。<ref name=Baueretal2012 />[[笼盖|笼盖]]为圆形，其下表面具极茂密的肉质长须，可长达2厘米。除此之外，笼盖无其他附属物。笼盖基部后方的[[笼蔓尾|笼蔓尾]]不分叉。<ref name=Clarke />

劳氏猪笼草的[[上位捕虫笼|上位笼]]非常特别，其下部为球形，中部剧烈收缩，上部为漏斗形。上位笼体型较大，可高达28厘米<ref name=P&L />，宽至10厘米。上位笼的笼翼大大缩窄。[[笼口|笼口]]边缘的唇仅剩下一系列[[唇肋|唇肋]]。上位笼内表面整体都为腺体区，无蜡质区。<ref>Cheek, M.R. & M.H.P. Jebb 2001. [[猪笼草科_(2001年专著)|Nepenthaceae]]. ''Flora Malesiana'' '''15''': 1–164.</ref>笼盖外翻，为卵形－椭圆形，可长达15厘米，宽至9厘米<ref name=Kurata />，无附属物。笼盖下表面具大量长约2厘米的长须。笼蔓尾和下位笼一样不分叉。<ref name=Clarke />劳氏猪笼草的上位笼非常坚硬，几乎是木质的。枯萎以后，仍可完好的保持形状。<ref name="夏洛特2007" /><ref name=P&L />

=== 花序与被毛 ===
劳氏猪笼草的[[花序|花序]]为[[总状花序|总状花序]]。[[总花梗|总花梗]]可长达20厘米，[[花序轴|花序轴]]可长达25厘米。[[花梗|花梗]]可长达20毫米，带两朵花，无[[苞片|苞片]]。<ref name=Kurata />[[萼片|萼片]]为长方形，可长达5毫米。<ref name=Clarke /><ref>Kaul, R.B. 1982. Floral and fruit morphology of ''Nepenthes lowii'' and ''N. villosa'', montane carnivores of Borneo. ''American Journal of Botany'' '''69'''(5): 793–803. {{DOI|10.2307/2442970}}</ref>一项对来自标本{{small|（''J.H.Adam 2406''、''J.H.Adam 2395''和''SAN 23341''，采集于海拔1700至2500米处）}}[[花粉|花粉]]大小的研究显示，其570粒花粉的平均直径为33.0微米{{small|（[[标准误|标准误]]为0.2，[[变异系数|变异系数]]为7.8%）}}。<ref>Adam, J.H. & C.C. Wilcock 1999. {{PDFlink|[http://psasir.upm.edu.my/3779/1/Palynological_Study_of_Bornean_Nepenthes_%28Nepenthaceae%29.pdf Palynological study of Bornean ''Nepenthes'' (Nepenthaceae).]}} ''Pertanika Journal of Tropical Agricultural Science'' '''22'''(1): 1–7.</ref>

劳氏猪笼草植株的大部分无毛被。仅花序、发育中的组织及叶片边缘具有棕色的短毛被。<ref name=Clarke />

== 生态关系 ==
=== 原生地 ===
劳氏猪笼草是[[婆罗洲|婆罗洲]]上许多相互隔离的山峰上[[特有种|特有的]]热带[[食虫植物|食虫植物]]。在[[沙巴|沙巴]]，劳氏猪笼草存在于[[基纳巴卢山|基纳巴卢山]]<ref name=Clarke />、[[坦布幼昆山|坦布幼昆山]]<ref name=Kurata />、[[阿兰伯山|阿兰伯山]]{{small|（Mount Alab）}}<ref name=AWS1992>Adam, J.H., C.C. Wilcock & M.D. Swaine 1992. {{PDFlink|[http://myais.fsktm.um.edu.my/8918/1/10.pdf The ecology and distribution of Bornean ''Nepenthes''.]}} ''Journal of Tropical Forest Science'' '''5'''(1): 13–25.</ref>、[[门塔波山|门塔波山]]{{small|（Mount Mentapok）}}<ref name=P&L />、[[莫库伯山|莫库伯山]]{{small|（Mount Monkobo）}}<ref name=Clarke />和[[特鲁斯马迪山|特鲁斯马迪山]]<ref name=P&L />。在[[沙捞越|沙捞越]]北部，其生长于[[阿比山|阿比山]]<ref name=AWS1992 />、[[布利山|布利山]]{{small|（Mount Buli}}<ref name=IUCN>{{IUCN2006|assessors=Clarke, C.M., R. Cantley, J. Nerz, H. Rischer & A. Witsuba|year=2000|id=39669|title=Nepenthes lowii|downloaded=10 May 2006}}</ref>、[[姆鲁山|姆鲁山]]<ref name=Clarke />、[[毛律山|毛律山]]<ref name=IUCN />、[[巴杜拉威山|巴杜拉威山]]<ref name=Sarawak />、[[霍斯山脉|霍斯山脉]]<ref name=IUCN />、[[塔玛阿布山脉|塔玛阿布山脉]]{{small|（Tama Abu Range）}}<ref name=IUCN />和[[峇里奧|峇里奧]]<ref name=IUCN />。<!--records from "Bukit Temedu in western Borneo and Gunung Rakik in eastern Borneo"<ref name=AWS1992 /> = N. ephippiata??-->劳氏猪笼草也存在于[[文莱|文莱]]，如在[[巴贡山|巴贡山]]海拔1650米至2600米的山顶地区。{{refn|在[[朱马特·哈吉·亚当|朱马特·哈吉·亚当]]、[[克里斯托弗·C·威尔科克|克里斯托弗·C·威尔科克]]和[[M·D·斯恩|M·D·斯恩]]{{small|（M. D. Swaine）}}1992年的文章中给出的劳氏猪笼草海拔分布范围为900米至3400米。<ref name=AWS1992 />|name=AWS1992|group="注"}}<ref name=Clarke /><ref name=J&C>Jebb, M.H.P. & M.R. Cheek 1997. [[猪笼草属（猪笼草科）的框架性修订|A skeletal revision of ''Nepenthes'' (Nepenthaceae)]]. ''[[布卢姆－植物分类学与植物地理学杂志|Blumea]]'' '''42'''(1): 1–106.</ref><ref name=McPherson />

[[Image:Murud_N._lowii_52.jpg|thumb]][[毛律山|毛律山]]山脊顶部的灌木丛中的劳氏猪笼草]]

劳氏猪笼草一般生长于土地贫瘠<ref name=Collins>Collins, N.M. 1980. The distribution of soil macrofauna on the west ridge of Gunung (Mount) Mulu, Sarawak. ''Oecologia'' '''44'''(2): 263–275. {{DOI|10.1007/BF00572689}}</ref>的山顶地区。其可陆生或附生。典型的原生地为[[苔藓森林|苔藓森林]]或矮小的山脊顶部植被区。<ref name=Clarke />劳氏猪笼草常常长于[[泥炭藓|泥炭藓]]中，基底由超基性岩、砂岩、花岗岩及石灰岩组成。<ref name=P&L />

在基纳巴卢山，劳氏猪笼草分布于东部山脊{{small|（East Ridge）}}、[[马西劳|东马西劳河]]及[[堪巴兰格|堪巴兰格]]地区。<ref name=Kurata />劳氏猪笼草曾分散分布于基纳巴卢山顶峰步道附近<ref>Toyoda, Y. 1972. {{PDFlink|[http://carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv01n4p62_63.pdf ''Nepenthes'' and I - Mt. Kinabalu (Borneo, Malaysia) Trip.]|116 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 118897 bytes -->}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''1'''(4): 62–63.</ref><ref>Malouf, P. 1995. {{PDFlink|[http://carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv24n3p64_69.pdf A visit to Kinabalu Park.]}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''24'''(3): 64–69.</ref><ref>Malouf, P. 1995. {{PDFlink|[http://carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv24n4p104_108.pdf A visit to Kinabalu Park.]}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''24'''(4): 104–108.</ref>海拔1970米至2270米的地区。<ref name=P&L />由于1997年至1998年的[[厄尔尼诺现象|厄尔尼诺现象]]造成的森林大火及登山者的破坏，基纳巴卢山顶峰步道附近的劳氏猪笼草多已死亡。现已很难在基纳巴卢山上发现劳氏猪笼草<ref name=Sabah>Clarke, C.M. 2001. ''[[沙巴的猪笼草指南|A Guide to the Pitcher Plants of Sabah]]''. Natural History Publications (Borneo), Kota Kinabalu.</ref><ref>Taylor, D.W. 1982. {{PDFlink|[http://www.carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv11n4p89_92.pdf Once In a Lifetime.]}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''11'''(4): 89–92.</ref>，“尚未确定”顶峰步道附近是否还存在劳氏猪笼草<ref name=Thong>Thong, J. 2006. {{PDFlink|[http://www.vcps.au.com/journals/81_Sep_2006Public.pdf Travels around North Borneo – Part 1.]}} ''[[维多利亚食虫植物协会杂志|Victorian Carnivorous Plant Society Journal]]'' '''81''': 12–17.</ref>。

产于特鲁斯马迪山的劳氏猪笼草变型<ref>Kitayama, K., J. Kulip, J. Nais & A. Biun 1993. Vegetation Survey on Mount Trus Madi, Borneo a Prospective New Mountain Park. ''Mountain Research and Development'' '''13'''(1): 99–105. {{DOI|10.2307/3673647}}</ref>可长出比基纳巴卢山产的劳氏猪笼草更大的捕虫笼<ref>Marabini, J. 1984. {{PDFlink|[http://www.carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv13n2p38_40.pdf A Field Trip to Gunong Trusmadi.]|442 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 453522 bytes -->}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''13'''(2): 38–40.</ref>。在毛律山，劳氏猪笼草生长于海拔1860米以上的地区。由于其恶劣的气候条件及缺乏植被保护，生于山顶的劳氏猪笼草一般都非常矮小。<ref>De Witte, J. 1996. {{PDFlink|[http://carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv25n2p41_45.pdf ''Nepenthes'' of Gunung Murud.]|567 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 581107 bytes -->}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''25'''(2): 41–45.</ref>

劳氏猪笼草在姆鲁山上随处可见。<ref name=Sabah />姆鲁山山顶的植被都很矮小，高度很少有超过1米。主要由[[杜鹃属|杜鹃属]]植物{{small|（特别是''Rhododendron ericoides''）}}<ref name=Steiner>Steiner, H. 2002. ''[[婆罗洲：山地及低地猪笼草|Borneo: Its Mountains and Lowlands with their Pitcher Plants]]''. Toihaan Publishing Company, Kota Kinabalu.</ref>及[[越橘属|越橘属]]{{small|（''Vaccinium''）}}和[[簇白珠属|簇白珠属]]{{small|（''Diplycosia''）}}植物组成<ref>Hanbury-Tenison, A.R. & A.C. Jermy 1979. The Rgs Expedition to Gunong Mulu, Sarawak 1977-78. ''The Geographical Journal'' '''145'''(2): 175–191. {{DOI|10.2307/634385}}</ref>。

